---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const today = new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-IN", { year: "numeric", month: "long", day: "numeric" });
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="SmashHit privacy policy — what data we collect and how we use it.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/" class="hover:text-slate-800">Home</a> › <span class="text-slate-700 font-medium">Privacy Policy</span></nav>
    <h1 class="font-[Barlow_Condensed] text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-8">Last updated: {today}</p>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>SmashHit (smashhit.in) does not collect personal data beyond what is strictly necessary to operate this site.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Analytics:</strong> We may use privacy-respecting analytics (such as Plausible or Fathom) to understand page traffic. No personally identifiable information is collected or stored.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Contact form:</strong> If you submit a message via our contact page, your name, email address, and message are stored solely to respond to your enquiry and are never shared with third parties.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Affiliate links:</strong> When you click an affiliate link, you are redirected to a third-party retailer (e.g. Amazon.in or Flipkart). Their privacy policies govern any data they collect.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Cookies:</strong> This site does not use tracking cookies. Third-party scripts (if any) may set their own cookies; refer to their respective privacy policies.</p>
      <p>For questions about this policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
